Body: Description: There is functionality to gain effective access for Group NTAccounts in the AIC but we have a need to produce these in bulk. Can you please advise if this is possible via MSSQL

Closest thing we have, is the FS_ShareAudit job in the Ad Hoc Audits folder in the FileSystem Group.

 

I'd configure for a test share and run it to review if thats what they are looking for.

Steps to Reproduce Updated: N/A
Mass reporting for groups?

What We've Learned Updated: The customer wants to be able to search by multiple resources. As they put it. if this page can be shown (i.e. this data exists in the DB) then there should be a way to produce this page 740 times without going to each individual resource. Custom SQL query or a custom report should do the trick.
